feat: initial project release (v1.0-alpha)

This monolithic commit encompasses the entire foundational architecture 
and UI/UX implementation built during the initial development session.

Architecture & Core:
- Next.js 16 App Router with TypeScript & Tailwind CSS v4
- Firebase Admin SDK integration
- Centralized Dictionary system (constants/dictionary.ts) for text management
- Strict TypeScript config (noUnusedLocals, noUnusedParameters)
- Comprehensive ANTIGRAVITY.md documentation

UI/UX & Components:
- Global Design System (globals.css) with Dark Mode & Brand Tokens
- Responsive Navbar with Mega Menu, Mobile Sidebar, and Scroll-aware Actions
- Dynamic Hero Section featuring Embla Carousel (HeroSlider)
- Social Proof UI: Google Stats Trust Badge with Verified Icon
- Social Proof UI: Infinite Scrolling Google Reviews Marquee (ReviewCard)
- Reusable UI primitives: Button, NavLink

SEO & Performance:
- Semantic HTML (article, anchor links instead of onClick)
- Next/Image optimization configurations (unoptimized for SVGs)
